    "ChatGPT may also have drawbacks.",
    "The increasing use of AI in writing raises questions about the role of humans in the writing process and job displacement (Halaweh, 2023).",
    "In an investigation of the potential implications of ChatGPT on the U.S. labor market, Eloundou et al. (2023) suggested that approximately 80% of the U.S. workforce could have at least 10% of their work tasks affected by the introduction of GPTs, while around 19% of workers may see at least 50% of their tasks impacted.",
    "Furthermore, work tasks performed by college educated workers are thought to be more likely to be replaced by LLMs than require manual labor (e.g., cooks, stonemasons; Eloundou et al., 2023).",
    "Many educators worry that AI-powered writing tools will replace the role of traditional writing tutors and editors, leading to job displacement and a loss of human connection in the writing process (Nazari et al., 2021)."
  ],
